    "Here are a few popular destinations for tourism marriages: * Hawaii, USA * Bali, Indonesia * Tuscany, Italy * Cancun, Mexico * Santorini, Greece * The Caribbean Islands * Las Vegas, USA * Paris, France * Bora Bora, French Polynesia * Kyoto, Japan It is important to consider that certain countries may have different requirements when it comes to getting legally married.",
    "Many couples may choose to get legally married in their native country, and have a symbolic wedding abroad at their destination of choice, in order to avoid any difficult paperwork or wait for long periods of time for information to be processed.",
    "Good Edit: (Modifications only include changes in scope of provided feedback) Tourism marriage, also known as \"tourism wedding\" or \"destination wedding,\" refers to the practice of couples traveling to a different location, often a popular tourist destination, to get married.",
    "Here are some key aspects of tourism marriages: 1.",
    "**Destination**: Couples choose a destination that holds special meaning to them or is a place they've always wanted to visit."
